# Suppress noisy diffs for pmos-emitted HTML artifacts. They carry an
# inline pmos-comments JSON block that mutates on every comment write,
# and a substantial inline <style> + <script> bundle. Marking them
# linguist-generated keeps the language-stats correct; -diff stops the
# default unified diff (use `git diff --text` to opt back in).
docs/pmos/**/*.html linguist-generated=true -diff
